title: An LFO alone does not a dubstep make
info:
So - it's about time someone uses a wobble-
bass for something other than dubstep ;)

Great thanks to the organizers of Revision!
You're doing an amazing job for everyone
to have this awesome party-experience.

It's an amazing party and this year,
and there's even coffee. AND IT'S FREE!

Not too much time and effort was put into
this tune compared to others I've done,
but we were in quite a rush with our
64k intro (and the music for it) so that
had highest priority.

Hope you enjoy anyways, and ...

P A N T S    O F F
